 --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Description
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This repository contains the chairman module for moodle. The module allows the management of
committees through the the control of current members, creation and viewing of agendas, scheduling
and organizing of meetings, central file storage for the committee, and much more. 

This version of the chairman module is compatible with Moodle 2.4.X.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Prerequisites
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Moodle Installed - Version 2.4.X

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 1. Copy comity folder into the <MoodleDirectory>/mod/
 2. Login as Administrator
 3. Install the new module in the standard plugin process


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For more informations, please go to the online documentation => http://oohoo.biz